Your stay at Magic Villa Luz is based on half board with buffet style breakfast and dinner, staying in a twin or double room with balcony. Superior rooms with kitchenette are available at a supplement.

Please note that some facilities may incur extra local charges. Checking in the rooms will be from 15:00hrs (earlier, depending on availability), checking out will be before 12:00hrs. On arrival the client will be asked for a credit card to guarantee against any damages. If clients do not wish to present one, they will be asked for a deposit.

